snippet.title: Bullet Echo Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Lead your team to victory in the new tactical pvp shooter from the creators of C.A.T.S.: Crash Arena Turbo Stars and King of Thieves! Unite with friends, set a strategy, and be the last team standing when the battle ends!

Get now for free:
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.zeptolab.bulletecho.google
Apple Store: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/bullet-echo/id1500726361

Bullet Echo Discord:  https://discord.gg/u4ApPB7
